  "concubinageNeutralTitle": "No option is universally better",
  "concubinageNeutralBody": "The choice between marriage and cohabitation depends on your situation: income, assets, children, canton, life plans. Marriage offers more automatic legal protections, cohabitation more flexibility. A specialist can help you see more clearly.",
  "concubinageChecklistIntro": "In cohabitation, nothing is automatic. Here are the essential protections to put in place to protect your partner.",
  "concubinageProtectionsEnPlace": "{count}/{total} protections in place",
  "@concubinageProtectionsEnPlace": {
